quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  14,19,"E a anndaa an ne…ó…óanke, wonnde Alla tagirii kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin goonga e wonnde tagiraali …óin meere? Si O muuyii ittugol on onon yim…ìe …ìen, O adda tagu goo ko rewa Mo …óoftoo Mo hara wanaa onon, O wa…óay …óum, tawde ko ko welani Mo fii."
  14,20,"Halkugol on adda wo…ó…ìe goo wonaali sattan…óum Alla. Ko O hattan…óo kala huunde. ronkintaa Mo."
  14,21,"tagu ngun yalta ka genaale ma…ì…ìe sutoo ka Alla √ëalnde Darngal. Lo'u…ìe jokkunoo…ìe koohoo…ìe …ìen wi'ana …ìen: Ko onon yo koohoo…ìe, menen ko men jokkunoo…ìe yamirooje mon, men ha…óitoo e ha…óaa…ói mon. Taw si on duncanay men e lepte Alla …óen go…ó…óum? Koohoo…ìe …ìen wi'a: Sinno Alla fewnuno men, men fewnayno on e …óum, da…óen en fow e lepte Makko …óen. Kono men majji, men majjinii on. Hino fotana'en nde lo'inoto…óen e ronnditagol lepte …óen maa nde mu√±√±oto…óen, tawde en alaa da…óirde e lepte …óen."
  14,22,"Ibuliisa wi'a, tuma nde yim…ìe Aljanna …ìen naati, yim…ìe Yiite …ìen kadi naati: Pellet Alla fodiino on fodoore goonga, O hunni ko O fodi on kon. Mi fodi on fodoore meere, mi ronki hunnude ko mi fodi on kon. Doole woo woodanaano lam aduna ko poo…óira on e keeferaaku e majjere. Kono le mi nodduno on e yeddugol, mi cu…óani on geddi …óin; yacci…óon e jokkugol lam. Haray wata on felam e majjere he…ìunde on nden; felee wonkiiji mon; ko kanji hanndi e feleede. Wanaa mi faabotoo…óo on du√±ana on lepte …óen; wanaa on faabotoo…ìe lam du√±angol …óe. Min mi yeddii ko kafidayno…óon lam kon e Alla ka dewe. Pellet, too√±irnoo…ìe sirkangol Alla …ìen aduna …ìe yeddi Mo, hino woodani …ìe lepte muusu…óe habbitii…óe …ìe √ëalnde Darngal."
  14,23,"Ko no seediri e too√±u…ìe …ìen, woni ko gom…óim…ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e …ìen naadirtee Aljannaaji, …ói can…ói ilata senngo leyd ku…ìeeje e le…ó…óe majji. Ko …ìe duumoray…ìe nder ton poomaa e du≈ãayee Joomi ma…ì…ìe. Hi…ìe hiwrondira hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen hiwroo…ìe, Joomi ma…ì…ìe kadi hiwrora …ìe "Salaam" (Kisiyee)."
  14,24,"E a yi'aali an Nulaa…óo, ko hono Alla piyiri misal konngol tawhiidi ngol: Rewetee…óo tanaa Allaahu alaa, Tuma O nanndani ngol e leggal welngal, woni du…ì…ìehi (tamoroowi) binndeere maggal on no irii ka leydi hino yarira ndiyam cal…ói maggal laa…ìu…ói, cal…ói maggal on no toowita ka weeyo, no yara caawa, foofa henndu laa…ìundu."